-- Swan Says Outlook for Business Investment in Australia Is `Very Strong'
-- James Paton
-- 2010-08-29T01:50:53Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-08-29/swan-says-outlook-for-business-investment-in-australia-is-very-strong-.html

          
          
             Australian Treasurer Wayne Swan said
that while “uncertainties and fragilities” remain in the
global economy, Australia is in a strong position.  
 There are signs construction is recovering in Australia,
and the outlook for business investment is “very strong,” Swan
said in his first weekly economic note since the Aug. 21
election.  
